  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Charan in the police who brutally killed the dog",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The suspect who brutally hacked a dog to death with a hand ax in Bunguduti, while he was absconding, surrendered at the village police station yesterday.",
        "He was produced by the police in Urgavariurai Court and has been remanded till the 29th.",
        "A few weeks ago, a video of a dog being brutally hacked to death with a hand axe, surfaced on social media. Investigations revealed that Bungudutivu took place in District 9.",
        "The police conducted investigations in this regard and arrested two persons aged 21 and 35 from the 9th district of Pungudutivu.",
        "The hand ax used to hack the dog to death and the mobile phone that recorded the video were also seized by the police.",
        "\"Due to drug addiction, we were involved in thefts in the town. When the dog saw us, it would betray us. Due to this, the police would call us for investigation as it is related to the thefts that take place there. That's why we killed that dog,\" he said.",
        "The court ordered the suspects to be produced before a medical examiner and remanded in custody after obtaining a report.",
        "Meanwhile, yesterday, Monday, the prime suspect surrendered at the Urgavariura police station. (R)"
      ],
